name: The Witness from the Inside of the Network
description: This little guy has been painted by an AI (GAN). On his way out of the network, he witnessed the discriminative network doing it's work. Finally arriving in the hands of the artist, he asked him to prepare this moment for the people in front of the screens and to greet you nicely. Made with the help of Artbreeder.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
